        "action": "Limit Mayoral positions to a maximum of two continuous terms ",
        "additional_details": "We believe limiting Mayoral positions to a maximum of two terms prevents a candidate from becoming encumbered. Nothing would prevent a candidate from seeking re-election again in the future but this would require that they must step down after a second term.",
        "background": "Bring forward a Bill to limit all Mayoral positions to a maximum of two continuous terms.",
